  "description": "Public marketing landing page for deal-room software positioning trust, security, and workflow velocity. Primary acquisition surface for enterprise sales.",
  "page_briefs": {
    "home": "Brand-variant hero anchors the page with bold headline on institutional trust and transaction velocity, supporting subhead, primary CTA for demo request, and a secondary CTA for security whitepaper. Below the hero, a features grid surfaces differentiators like granular permissions, watermarking, and audit trail. A testimonials band shows logos and quotes from PE and investment banking customers. The closing CTA section drives toward booking an enterprise demo."
